						<div class="postbody">Are there actually two of these? This is my confusion.<br /><br />I thought these samples were only allowed within $C000-$FFFF. But, when searching for the cheering dpcm during the intro to Mike Tysons Punch Out, its located within a bank that is used with $A000-$BFFF. I was able to have that sample, within the Capcom 6c80 sound engine I'm using for a new project.<br /><br />So do I have the right info? Are there dpcm and pcm?<br /><br />Thanks for reading!</div>

